gridftp-dsi-posix
=================

Formerly the xrootd-dsi package, renamed upstream since no
XRootD-related functions are actually used for this posix DSI
implementation.

This package requires Globus source in order to build.

Source can be found at:
https://github.com/wyang007/gridftp_dsi_posix
git archive --prefix=gridft-posix-dsi-{VERSION}/ {GIT REVISION} | gzip -9 > gridftp-posix-dsi-{VERSION}.tar.gz
